      "author": "kotserge",
      "description": "# 1.0.0 — Initial release\r\n\r\nAdds a Kanban view to Obsidian Bases. Configure any base with a group-by property to lay it out as a board: groups become columns, matching notes become cards.\r\n\r\n## Features\r\n- Columns driven by the base's group-by property\r\n- Cards show visible Bases properties, rendered with native formatting\r\n- Drag and drop cards between columns to update the group-by value in frontmatter\r\n- Click a card to open the note; Ctrl/Cmd-click to open in a new tab\r\n- Notes missing the group-by property appear in an \"Uncategorized\" column\r\n- Works on desktop and mobile",
